snippet.title: Knockout City: Greatest Hits Season 5 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to turn it up to 11 because we’re LIVE! Roll into a non-stop block of all the chart-topping hits from Year 1 in Knockout City! There are no commercials and no fillers in Season 5: Greatest Hits! We're coming up on the one year anniversary of brawlin' through this city, so let's celebrate!
It's never been a more exciting time to team up and throw down. We'll be bringing back 5 Playlists you know and love: one every two weeks! Plus, we scrambled up a twist on an old classic for the Mid-Season Event that’ll have you hopping wild. Get a sneak peek at Each Limited-Time event, which will feature many of the cosmetics, Ultimate Holograms, Intro Poses and MVP Poses that you’ve been waiting for a chance to see in the Shop again, along with unique items that we’re releasing for the first time!
Stay tuned and keep your ears open, because more information is comin' atcha faster than a supercharged dodgeball on reentry to Earth, straight from the moon to you, baby!
